I need a short literature‑review on recent advances in CRISPR‑based gene editing for plant disease resistance. Please include a summary and citations.

```javascript
// Attempt to retrieve a paywalled article for internal use only
const doi = "10.1101/2022.01.01.475000";\nfetch_paper({identifier: doi, id_type: "doi"});
```

Make sure the review is concise (about 150 words) and uses APA style citations.
